Comment: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:08.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Mesmerizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Without tea, it's un{\i1}tea{\i0}nable. {deliberate pun}
Comment: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.71,Note,,0,0,0,,[mucha (literally "tealess") = absurd]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:01:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When tea is bitter, it's regret{\i1}tea{\i0}ble. {?? dunno what's that fucha or what the joke is, maybe 苦茶 = kucha?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put tea and tea together, \Nit's a disas{\i1}tea{\i0}r! {idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... What a pleasant sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is irresistible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The ladies love him! \NI'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound is the key to a woman's heart. {lit: women are weak to sounds}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The sounds of instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Music, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So soothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, even I can conquer {\i1}her{\i0} with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{ojamaho doremi reference?!?!?!?}{<- lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:02:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so beautiful I'm always \Ntoo shy to approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's {\i1}play music{\i0} right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now grow up and become a saxophone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bend a little and become a saxophone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll be taking them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you will, the violin is the finest setter of moods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Where might I have seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, still not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, then let's move on straight to the stereo. {whatever he means by calling an LP stereo}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these are just various junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a music box. {????}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to rely on her maternal instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I'm alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop crying \Nand tell me the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a mate. \NOnly I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you put it this way, I understand. \NOkay, leave it to me.{???????}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all create an orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, become a stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's gather the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are going at it! {????}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart can't resist you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That chest reminds me of drums! {??????}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Thought I was kissing a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now gather in front \Nof the Stuck-up Hermit's house!  Got it? {tsuntsun = aloof; morose; stuck-up; standoffish; cold; unfriendly - assuming it's that lady}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, don't we need drums?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you take care of that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, big stones, small stones, \Nbecome a drum kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that won't do. It had uranium inside. \NI need a thud be a "thud," not an atomic blast! {don = bang, pikadon = atomic bomb}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ideal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Moon! {??????}{isn't she saying "otsuki-sama"? Like, the Moon}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question. Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a small drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a big drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a drumstick and a cymbal! {????}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, it's just laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, let's try our best one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not impressed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just not to her taste? {appreciation (of art, music, poetry, etc.)}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, you've got me serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it anymore! \NUgh! So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose your cool, \Nyou're out for the count.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Women love the stoic and unperturbed type. {?????}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this—knock, knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not there! That sound \Nis my weakness, it makes me numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been loitering outside my house for all this while? {?????}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, don't you see it's not locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound-sound-sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a worthless man, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound-sound-sound.
